---
title: Honey-Lemon Halloumi & Jewelled Couscous with Garden Salad & Herby Mayo
description: Halloumi is truly the king of cheeses, don’t you think? Salty, squeaky and pan-fried to golden deliciousness, it’s always a winner. Tonight, we’re adding lemon and honey for sweet and tangy goodness. And for something extra special, we’ll serve it alongside a bejewelled couscous, with vibrant carrot and sweet currants speckled throughout.

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with tomato due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/676912fe9bfc6de73c8e4707-f4398033.jpeg
